libftxf is a library for Transactional NTFS (TxF) data types.

Project information:

* Status: experimental
* Licence: LGPL-3.0-or-later

For more information see:

* Project documentation: https://github.com/libyal/libftxf/wiki/Home
* How to build from source: https://github.com/libyal/libftxf/wiki/Building

